ns (Step C3) |\n| `gh run list/view/download *` | Poll + download re-run results |\n| `gh pr create *` | Create flaky-fix PRs (Step 4b) |\n| `gh issue list/create/comment *` | Manage real-bug issues (Step 4b) |\n| `git checkout/add/commit/push *` | Branch + commit + push for PRs |\n| `git diff/log/status*` | Inspect repo state during analysis |\n\n**What's excluded:** `gh repo *`, `gh release *`, `git reset *`, `git rebase *`, `git merge *`, `git branch -D *`, and any other destructive operations.\n\n## Verification\n```bash\ngit push\ngh workflow run e2e-triage.yml --ref alisha/e2e-triage -f run_id=22772950740\n```\n\n\nIf you need specific details from before exiting plan mode (like exact code snippets, error messages, or content you generated), read the full transcript at: /Users/alisha/.claude/projects/-Users-alisha-Projects-devenv-cli/d78a956d-b1f9-4dcc-8055-ac01eb1a9769.jsonl\n\n---\n\nTool loaded.\n\n---\n\nTool loaded."